[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1081[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## Step 5: Cache and Serve Results
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1082[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1083[0m:[38;5;10m[49m *The pseudocode calls this `serve_interaction_check(request)`. Clinical systems need sub-second response times. We cache the raw interaction paths (before patient-specific scoring) so that repeated checks for common drug combinations skip the graph traversal entirely. Patient-specific scoring is fast (just arithmetic), so we apply it fresh each time.*
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1084[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1085[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```python
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1086[0m:[38;5;10m[49m redis_client = redis.Redis(host=REDIS_HOST, port=REDIS_PORT, decode_responses=True)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1087[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1088[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1089[0m:[38;5;10m[49m def serve_interaction_check(request: dict) -> dict:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1090[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1091[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Entry point for clinical system interaction checks. Handles caching
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1092[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     to ensure sub-second response times for common drug combinations.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1093[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1094[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     The caching strategy: we cache the raw interaction paths (the graph
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1095[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     traversal results) keyed by the sorted set of RxCUIs. Patient context
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1096[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     is NOT part of the cache key because it varies per patient. We re-apply
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1097[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     patient-specific scoring on every request, which is fast (just math).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1098[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1099[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     This means a cache hit still produces patient-specific results. The
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1100[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     expensive part (graph traversal) is cached; the cheap part (scoring)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1101[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     runs fresh.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1102[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1103[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Args:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1104[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         request: Dict with:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1105[0m:[38;5;10m[49m             - medications: List of medication dicts (rxcui, name, dose, etc.)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1106[0m:[38;5;10m[49m             - patient_context: Optional patient factors dict
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1107[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1108[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Returns:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1109[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         Interaction check results (same format as check_interactions).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1110[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
