[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1123[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1124[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     # Generate cache key from sorted RxCUIs.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1125[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     # Sorting ensures the same drug set always produces the same key
