[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1179[0m:[38;5;10m[49m def invalidate_cache():
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1180[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1181[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Flush the interaction cache. Call this after loading new source data
