[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1183[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1184[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     In production, you'd use a more targeted approach: track which drugs
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1185[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     were affected by the update and only invalidate cache keys containing
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1186[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     those RxCUIs. But for weekly full rebuilds, flushing everything is simpler.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1187[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1188[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     # SCAN for all keys with our prefix and delete them.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1189[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     cursor = 0
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1190[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     deleted = 0
